For the future, I advi&s;e you to be more
&s;paring of hard words: Since, as you in|cautiou&s;ly
deal them about, they may
chance to light on your friends as well as
your adver&s;aries. As for my part, I &s;hall
not retaliate. It is &s;ufficient to &s;ay you are
